Class DefaultContentResolver

java.lang.Object
  com.github.cwilper.fcrepo.dto.core.io.DefaultContentResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentResolver
public class DefaultContentResolver
extends Object
implements ContentResolver

A ContentResolver that resolves http[s] and local file URIs.

NOTE: This resolver only works with relative URIs when a base URI is also provided.
